    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Honda Smart Key System Structure Description - Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Honda Smart Key System enables the driver to lock/unlock the doors and tailgate and start the engine with the Honda Smart Key. The LF-RF communication method is used for the communication system: LF (Low Frequency) signals are transmitted from the LF antenna, and the RF (Radio Frequency) signals from the Honda Smart Key are received by the RF unit built into the Smart ECU."
    },
